  <brief_title>Effects of Omega-3 Fatty Acid Supplementation on Inflammatory Response in Multisystem Trauma Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Omega-3 Fatty Acid Supplementation on Inflammatory Response in Multisystem Trauma Patients</official_title>
